(Project artifact.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(KAVAL + ALGHOSAZI FIPPLE FLUTES) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This repository is a build-ready design packet for two related long fipple flutes:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- a **Moldavian/Romanian-style fipple kaval** family, including 5-hole, 7-hole, two-piece, and) Tj
T*
(double-drone options;) Tj
T*
(- a **fipple Alghosazi** family inspired by the Anasazi/Basketmaker long-flute lineage, with) Tj
T*
(an easier fipple head and a rear thumb hole.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The head design intentionally borrows from Tony's fujara CAD: the player blows into an end) Tj
T*
(mouth inlet, the air travels through a controlled internal flue, and sound is made at a side) Tj
T*
(**true sound window** and splitting edge. The head is not copied from a commercial maker; it) Tj
T*
(is a Tony-shop fujara/NAF hybrid that can be tuned and rebuilt.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(BUILD FIRST) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
