T*
(pattern.  |) Tj
T*
(|  ALG-AS3-J2  |  Best first Alghosazi: published 82 cm two-piece precedent, thumb-hole) Tj
T*
(layout.  |) Tj
T*
(|  P0-FIPPLE-HEAD  |  Scrap head tile that proves the mouth inlet, flue, window, and splitting) Tj
T*
(edge before a full body.  |) Tj
